{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Wawancara Dengan Developer Game Indonesia Tamatin Entertainment","content":"<p><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bekraf-game-prime-dari-tahun-ke-tahun/\">BEKRAF Game Prime</a> jadi ajang bagi para <em>developer</em> game Indonesia untuk unjuk gigi. Setiap tahunnya, para <em>developer</em> menyiapkan game mereka yang paling keren untuk ditampilkan kepada khalayak ramai.</p>\n<p>Tim CIAYO Blog berkesempatan untuk mewawancarai salah satu <em>developer</em> game yang bakal hadir di Game Prime 2018. Kontributor Meka berbicara dengan Yodi Pramudito, CEO dari studio game <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tamatinentertainment/?ref=br_rs\">Tamatin Entertainment</a> asal kota Bandung. Apa yang bakal dihadirkan Tamatin di Game Prime tahun ini?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49036\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49036\" data-attachment-id=\"49036\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/01-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49036\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49036\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment</p></div>\n<h1>Bagaimana awalnya Tamatin Entertainment berdiri?</h1>\n<p>Kami mulai bikin game bareng-bareng pertama kali sudah dari 2014 sebenernya, cuma itu untuk lomba-lomba aja dan sambil kuliah. Setelah itu sempet vakum dan sisa saya doang, tapi 2016 tengah saya ajak-ajakin lagi untuk mulai serius.</p>\n<h1>Sampai saat ini sudan merilis berapa game?</h1>\n<p>Sampai sekarang sih produk yang rilis baru dua, <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.TamatinEntertainment.HyperSpaceSurvivor\">Hyperspace Crystalz</a> dan <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tamatinent.tamakinc&amp;hl=in\">Tamak Inc</a>. Kalau dari project luar, untuk game baru sedikit sih. Paling banyak <em>edugame</em> bareng BPOM tahun 2016. Tahun 2017 kita sempet bantu di Azure Saga, Masshive, dan game Crimson451 dari Visionesia Studio. Sisanya banyak aplikasi-aplikasi interaktif sih.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49037\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49037\" data-attachment-id=\"49037\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/02-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49037\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: BEKRAF Game Prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/02-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49037\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: BEKRAF Game Prime</p></div>\n<h1>Apa saja prestasi yang sudah diraih Tamatin Entertainment?</h1>\n<p>Dulu pas <em>event</em> In-Game 2015 game kami Particle Dash sempat jadi <em>nominee</em> Most Innovative Game.</p>\n<h1>Dengar-dengar, kalian lagi bikin game baru yang namanya Kronika. Bisa diceritakan tentang gamenya?</h1>\n<p>Kronika gampangnya bisa dbiliang game <em>action-adventure</em> yang memiliki fokus lebih di elemen <em>local co-op</em>-nya, dengan cerita dan dunianya sendiri tentunya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49038\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49038\" data-attachment-id=\"49038\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/03-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49038\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/03-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49038\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment</p></div>\n<h1>Seperti apa cerita dan dunia dari Kronika?</h1>\n<p>Kronika bererita tentang seorang gadis, bersama dengan teman-teman yang ditemui sepanjang perjalanan, yang berusaha mencari kembali adiknya yang diculik saat desanya diserang oleh pasukan bersenjata.</p>\n<p>Dunianya sendiri secara teknologi masih ada di era <em>medieval</em> gitu, tapi karena ada <em>magic</em> juga, jadi teknologi yang ada juga berhubungan dengan <em>magic</em> itu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49039\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49039\" data-attachment-id=\"49039\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/04-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49039\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/04-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49039\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment</p></div>\n<h1>Bagaimana dengan <em>gameplay</em>-nya?</h1>\n<p>Nah, dari <em>gameplay</em>-nya sendiri, meskipun banyak terinspirasi dari game Zelda 2D, kita berusaha bikin sesuatu hal yang unik juga. Fokus utama <em>gameplay</em>-nya berputar di <em>positioning</em>, <em>timing</em> dan <em>coordination</em>. Hampir nggak ada elemen RPG-nya, soalnya banyak yang nanya ini RPG apa bukan. Kronika juga punya sistem unik yang kita sebut &#8220;<em>helping hand</em>.&#8221; Jadi nanti sepanjang permainan akan ada beberapa aksi yang harus dilakukan oleh 2 pemain untuk dieksekusi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49040\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49040\" data-attachment-id=\"49040\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/05-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49040\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/05-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49040\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment</p></div>\n<h1>Rencananya, Kronika bakal rilis di platform apa saja?</h1>\n<p>Pinginnya PC dan konsol, dan kalau bisa Nintendo Switch sih. Dari sekarang kita sudah berusaha sesuaikan kontrol <em>gameplay</em>-nya agar bisa dimainkan hanya pakai 1 Joycon Nintendo Switch saja.</p>\n<h1>Apa nanti Kronika bakal punya versi demo yang bisa dimainkan?</h1>\n<p>Kita mau riset dulu, kalau game kayak Kronika ini apakah direkomendasikan untuk bikin versi <em>demo playable</em> atau nggak. Tapi nanti Kronika bisa dimainkan di Game Prime 2018, kami sangat membutuhkan banyak <em>test player.</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49041\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49041\" data-attachment-id=\"49041\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/06-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49041\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/06-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49041\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tamatin Entertainment</p></div>\n<h1>Gimana pengalaman kalian selama mengikuti <em>event</em> Game Prime sebelumnya?</h1>\n<p><em>Nice</em> sih, kita selalu buka <em>booth</em> kalau ada. Awalnya kita ikutan untuk seru-seruan aja, tapi sekarang berguna banget buat cari <em>public feedback</em> dan <em>networking</em> dengan <em>developer</em> lain.</p>\n<h1>Apa saja dampak positif dari <em>event</em> seperti Game Prime untuk <em>developer</em> game lokal?</h1>\n<p><em>Networking</em>, ya. Kita kenal banyak orang dan juga <em>opportunity</em> baru yang kita ga tau. Contoh solidnya, Game Prime 2 tahun lalu saya pertama kali ketemu komikus Komik Ga Jelas (Jasmine Surkatty) dan tahun berikutnya kita bawa game bareng-bareng.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_49042\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49042\" data-attachment-id=\"49042\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/wawancara-dengan-tamatin-entertainment/attachment/07-tamatin-entertainment/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-tamatin-entertainment\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-49042\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Komik Ga Jelas\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/07-tamatin-entertainment-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49042\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Komik Ga Jelas</p></div>\n<h1>Yodi punya pesan untuk teman-teman developer yang baru terjun ke dunia game?</h1>\n<p>Industri <em>game dev</em> di Indonesia lagi berkembang; memang belum stabil, tapi berkembang cukup oke sih. Jadi kalau mau kerja di dunia game lokal ya harus senang dan konsisten. Kalau nggak bisa, coba pikir-pikir lagi deh. Bukan bermaksud menakut-nakuti, cuma kalau lu memang senang dan belum banyak tuntutan dalam waktu relatif dekat (2-4 tahun), mungkin <em>game dev</em> bisa jadi pengalaman yang sangat berharga.</p>\n<p>Kalau saya boleh titip pesan, saya pribadi belakangan kurang merekomendasikan orang untuk <em>&#8220;risk it all,&#8221;</em> terjun ke dunia <em>game dev</em> dengan <em>drop</em> sekolah, ngabisin tabungan, dan lain-lain. Hidup nggak cuma di kerjaan doang. Pastikan kebutuhan utama terpenuhi dulu.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Itu dia <em>chit-chat</em> singkat CIAYO Blog bersama Tamatin Entertainment! Penasaran dengan Kronika dan game-game keren lain buatan developer Indonesia? Jangan sampai ketinggalan Game Prime 2018! Pesan tiket gratisnya sekarang juga di <a href=\"http://bit.ly/bgp2018\">bit.ly/bgp2018</a>.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"498d4722-1671-50ef-912a-9786e475c5f1"}}}